            <who name="Sebastian Werner">info</who>
            <bug_when>2009-03-23 15:07:40 +0100</bug_when>
            <thetext>When opening this example:
application/demobrowser/source/index.html#widget~TabView.html

one see that the tabs render a huge space between the icons and the label. This is a major change as it was less than half the space in 0.8. It looks quite bad now when using 16 or 22 pixel icons.

Maybe this is related to the added close symbol support.

Normally we had a 4 pixel space between icon and label on tabs (atoms, ...) and this looks good for icon sizes between 16px and 32px. The distance to the close button should maybe higher, but this could be reolved with some kind of margin as well.</thetext>
